data.description: Nestled in the bustling heart of Des Moines, this captivating ranch-style home offers 3-bedrooms, 1-bathroom. Enjoy the warmth of hardwood floors throughout and bask in the natural light streaming through the large bay window in the living room. The eat-in kitchen, fully equipped with all appliances, becomes the heart of the home. Venture downstairs to discover a versatile 4th non-conforming room in the finished basement, ideal for various uses. Outside, a fenced backyard adds a touch of privacy, and the spacious yard encourages outdoor activities. The front deck invites relaxation and neighborhood connection. This home seamlessly blends practicality with a cozy ambiance. All information obtained from Seller and public records.
